24. Sept 2013
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Merged with public release 1.2
   Added QPX-optimization to modules/linalg/cmatrix.c

   Details of merge:
   -----------------
   Deleted CFLAGS and CC from C2:
   - devel/dirac/Makefile      
   - devel/linalg/Makefile     
   - devel/sap/Makefile	      
   - devel/sw_term/Makefile    
   - main/Makefile
    
   Adjusted calls to mpc_bcast:
   - main/ms1.c		      
   - main/ms2.c		      
   - main/ms4.c		      
   - main/qcd1.c		      
   - main/qcd2.c		      
   - main/ym1.c		      
   - modules/archive/sarchive.c
   - modules/flags/dfl_parms.c 
   
   Merged conflicts between QPX and AVX (with mul_pauli2)
   - modules/dirac/Dw.c
   
   Merged conflicts between use of MPI_* and mpc_bcast
   - modules/linalg/salg_dble.c
   
   Merged conflicts in #ifdef logics (now separate #ifdef AVX / #else for mul_pauli2)
   - modules/sw_term/pauli.c   
   
   Added QPX optimisation from Dalibor
   - modules/linalg/cmatrix.c 
   
   Further cleanings:
   - include/qpx.h           (renamed temporary variables v* to qpx_r*)
   - modules/dirac/Dw.c      (added declaration of v11 ... v23, removed others)
   - modules/dirac/Dw_dble.c (added declaration of v11 ... v23, removed others)
   - modules/linalg/salg.c   (dropped unused res21)

