    Additional support for optimization (global sums) and tuning (memory usage)
    - replaced double precision global sums by mpc_gsum_d
      (except in devel and modules/update/hmc.c)
    - replaced broadcast by mpc_bcast_?
      (except in devel)
    - added amem_*_mb functions in utils.c (and utils.h)
    - added mpc_* functions in utils.c (and utils.h)
    - added call to mpc_print_info and amem_*_mb in qcd1.c

